    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in good condition. It runs and drives well with no major mechanical issues. The exterior has minor wear \u2014 a few small scratches and light scuffs \u2014 but no significant dents or structural damage. The interior is intact and functional. Overall a solid, reliable vehicle with normal signs of use.",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a solid everyday driver at a reasonable price? This vehicle falls squarely in the 'fair' category \u2014 it has some visible wear on the exterior and the interior shows its age, but the key mechanical components are functional and it's ready to get you where you need to go. It's not a showroom beauty, but it's an honest, dependable option for budget-conscious buyers who want reliable transportation without the premium price tag. Come take a look \u2014 what you see is exactly what you get!",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition and priced to reflect exactly that \u2014 it's a dependable, drivable car for buyers who want transportation without paying a premium. The exterior shows visible signs of age and use: expect faded paint in places, some surface scratches, and possibly minor dents or dings that haven't been touched up. The interior is functional but worn \u2014 the upholstery, trim, and controls show everyday use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though we'd recommend budgeting for some maintenance items in the near future, as is typical for a vehicle at this stage of its life. There are no major hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get. This is an honest, straightforward deal for a buyer with realistic expectations and a practical mindset.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 a rare find in the used car market. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint retains a deep, lustrous shine with no visible scratches, chips, dents, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and consistent, all trim pieces are perfectly intact, and the glass is clear and crack-free. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 every surface is clean, fresh, and shows virtually no signs of wear. Seats, carpets, headliner, and dashboard all look and feel as though the vehicle has barely been used. All controls, buttons, and features function exactly as intended, with no quirks or issues to report. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. Mechanically, the vehicle is in top-tier shape \u2014 brakes, suspension, tires, and all systems are in excellent working order. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged; we are confident this car will exceed expectations. This is a genuine opportunity to own a used vehicle that truly rivals new-car quality.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A solid, dependable choice for the discerning buyer who wants quality without the new-car premium. This vehicle presents beautifully \u2014 clean interior, well-maintained mechanicals, and a road-ready exterior that reflects careful ownership. Every mile has been driven with care, and it shows. Whether you're commuting daily or hitting the open road on weekends, this is a car you can count on. Come see it in person and feel the difference that genuine quality makes. Priced to move at exceptional value.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! \ud83d\ude97 I've got a fantastic ride here that I'm genuinely excited to pass along to its next happy owner. This beauty is in great shape \u2014 she's been well cared for, drives smooth, and turns heads wherever she goes. Sure, she's got a little character from everyday life (what well-loved car doesn't?), but nothing that gets in the way of a fantastic driving experience. I've always believed in being straight with folks, and I can honestly say this is a solid, dependable car that's ready to serve you well for years to come. Whether you're commuting, road-tripping, or just cruising on a sunny afternoon, this one won't let you down. Come take her for a spin \u2014 I think you'll fall in love just like I did. Let's find her a great new home!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Rolling out of our lot is this sharp, road-ready machine that's been living its best life under the hood. The powertrain delivers crisp throttle response with no hesitation across the RPM band \u2014 exactly what you want when you need confident highway merging or spirited weekend driving. The suspension geometry remains tight with no perceptible play in the steering rack, giving you that connected, planted feel through corners. Braking hardware is fully operational with solid pedal feel and progressive bite. Interior appointments show the kind of honest wear you'd expect from a well-used but well-loved daily driver \u2014 functional, comfortable, and driver-focused. All primary systems \u2014 HVAC, infotainment, power accessories \u2014 are operating as designed. This is a mechanically sound, turn-key example that won't leave you chasing gremlins. Priced to reflect its strong mechanical foundation and move quickly for the right buyer.",
      "price": 37500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs strong. Looks clean. No nonsense, no surprises. Ready to drive today.",
      "price": 37500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here's a car that's lived a real life and has the soul to prove it. This beauty carries the kind of honest road miles that speak to a well-traveled companion \u2014 reliable, ready, and full of character. The interior tells stories of morning commutes and weekend escapes, while the engine hums with the confidence of a machine that's been driven, not babied. Yes, there are the natural signs of a life well-used \u2014 a scuff here, a scratch there \u2014 but nothing that diminishes the genuine pleasure of sliding behind the wheel and feeling the road open up ahead of you. Mechanically sound and road-ready, this is the car for someone who values substance over showroom shine. Drive it daily, drive it proudly. Come see it in person \u2014 it won't disappoint.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This well-maintained vehicle presents an excellent opportunity for the savvy buyer seeking dependable, everyday transportation without the premium price tag of a newer model. Showing the kind of honest wear you'd expect from a conscientiously owned car, it runs smoothly and has been kept in solid mechanical shape. Clean interior, responsive handling, and a reliable drivetrain make this a smart, practical choice. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we're confident it will impress.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    }
  ],
